<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-08-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="513" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d513">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Uruguay</gloss>
                                to President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Montevideo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-08-10"><hi rend="italic">August 10,
                                1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I have just given the first hand-shaking to Secretary of State Elihu
                            Root. I salute you with lively sentiments of American brotherhood.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">José Batlle y
                            Ordonez.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>